{"comments":"Color properties - measurable characteristics.\n\nPerceptual properties for color analysis:\n- **Colorfulness**: How vivid/chromatic a color appears\n- **Brightness**: Simple average RGB brightness\n- **Perceived Lightness**: L* from CIELAB (perceptually uniform)\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Perceived colorfulness (chroma relative to lightness)\n\nA measure of how vivid a color appears. Highly saturated colors\nat mid-lightness have maximum colorfulness.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","HSL"],"HSL"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[51,34],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Properties.purs","start":[51,1]},"title":"colorfulness"},{"children":[],"comments":"Chroma - saturation normalized to 0-1 range\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","HSL"],"HSL"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[58,28],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Properties.purs","start":[58,1]},"title":"chroma"},{"children":[],"comments":"Simple brightness (average of RGB channels)\n\nReturns 0-1 range. This is a naive measure; use perceivedLightness\nfor perceptually accurate results.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Co